document.topic_text: By Joanmarie Curran, Broker Home of the Day is presented by the Puget Sound Business Journal with Realogics Sotheby's International Realty. This is your invitation to view some of Seattle's most-luxurious properties. Come inside and take a look around. Click on the gallery image to view today's featured property. 407 Wana Wana Place NE, Tacoma, WA 98422 | $525,000 Sophisticated appointments in every corner, just right spaces for everyone. Open Great Room floor plan opens to back yard and BBQ deck.… ...
